    "Name": "Dragon",
    "Details": "This Custom Dragon was piloted by Warlord Syovo Yorioshi from 25th May to 26th September 3025 during the Battle of Galtor III. Only the left-arm mounted Medium Laser remains, with Large Laser in the right arm and an SRM4 and Flamer mounted in the Center. A Small Laser was also installed next to the Cockpit, with an additional 5 Heat Sinks and 3 more tons of armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>",
